Craig Wright is an Australian Bitcoin enthusiast. In December 2015 articles in Wired (1.1) and Gizmodo (1.2) pointed to him as a possible candidate for the identity of [[Satoshi_Nakamoto]].

These claims, despite being echoed by media worldwide, were debunked on December 11th 2015 by anyone with basic knowledge of Google Cache.


